FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Everything you need to know about our marble marketplace
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: How does the marble marketplace work?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our marketplace connects marble sellers with buyers. Users can list their marbles for sale, browse available marbles, and make purchases securely through our platform.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: What types of marbles can I find on the marketplace?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: We offer a wide variety of marbles, including antique, handmade, collectible, and modern designs. You can find glass, clay, stone, and even rare materials like agate or onyx.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: How do I ensure the quality of the marbles I purchase?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Sellers are required to provide detailed descriptions and high-quality images of their marbles. We also have a rating system and buyer protection policy to ensure a satisfactory experience.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: Can I sell my own marble collection on the marketplace?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Absolutely! Creating a seller account is easy and free. Once verified, you can list your marbles, set prices, and manage your inventory through our user-friendly dashboard.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: What payment methods are accepted on the marble marketplace?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: We accept major credit cards, PayPal, and select cryptocurrencies. All transactions are processed securely to protect both buyers and sellers.

ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Our marketplace offers a wide variety of marbles, including antique, handmade, collectible, and modern designs. You can find everything from classic cat's eyes to rare vintage marbles.

ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: We have a verification process for sellers and encourage detailed descriptions and high-quality images. Additionally, our user rating system and dispute resolution service help ensure a trustworthy buying experience.
